The walls resemble a white driven snow, although the room is comfortably warm. Coming from a corner in the ceiling is a strong and concentrated pillar of light that shines down to the floor below. On the opposite side of the room is a large and thick rope that suspends a weight. The weight seems to be keeping a contraption in place that is blocking the way out to the North.
#ROOM_STATE_1#
The room has a pillar of light and a rope mechanism holding the door shut on the opposite side of the room.
#ROOM_STATE_2#
With the last thread of the rope breaking, the obstruction swings heavily aside and slams against the wall, clearing the path to the North.